CloudGear is a simple iPhone app that allows you to manage your Amazon EC2 instances.
And it allows you to:
- Search the AMI directory, it covers the Amazon, public and self-owned AMIs.
- Launch, Start, stop and terminate ebs and instance-store based EC2 instances.
- Monitor the network and CPU usages using Amazon Cloud Watch.
- Custom Launch of EC2 instances.
- List ebs devices and attach them to running EC2 instances.
- Securely store the keys in the keychain.
- Update and delete your amazon access and private keys from your iPhone.

CloudGear is compatible with iOS 3.2 or later.